snippet.title: Amber Heard's Heartbreaking Testimony As a Survivor of Domestic Abuse
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's heartbreaking testimony in which she details one of the many times raging alcoholic Johnny Depp abused her. 

The evidence she has presented, almost 300 pages of pictures, videos and text messages is overwhelming. You can read the full document here: https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/5835867-Amber-Heard-Motion-to-Dismiss.html

No matter how much Depp's acolytes try to twist the facts and make him see like the victim, there's a lot of evidence she endured a long period of time as a victim of domestic abuse, verbal, emotional and physical, before she decided to defend herself and "not be doormat."

#ForeverTeamAmberHeard
#JusticeForAmberHeard
